@title Interface for the AI services mnager on Doctrina
 @author DoctrinaAI (Tillo Bekov)

@dev Gets the list of all Doctus in the registry
 
 @return dids Array of Doctus IDs

devdoc.author: DoctrinaAI (Tillo Bekov)

addDoctusMembers(bytes32,address[]).details: Adds new members to the Doctus      Only the owner can add new members

changeDoctusMetadataURI(bytes32,bytes).details: Updates the metadata for the Doctus      Only the owner can update the metadata

changeDoctusOwner(bytes32,address).details: Updates the owner of Doctus.       Only the owner can call this function. Reverts if the id is not found.

createDoctus(bytes32,bytes,address[]).details: Adds a new Doctus. Reverts if the given Doctus id (did) has already been registered.

params.did: id of the Doctus to create, must be unique.
params.members: Array of member addresses to seed the Doctus with.
params.metadataURI: MetadataURI of Doctus to create, must be unique.

createService(bytes32,bytes32,bytes).details: Create a new Service under the Doctus      Only the Doctus owner can create a new Service

params.sid: Unique ID for the new Service

deleteDoctus(bytes32).details: Deleted the Doctus       Only the owner can delete the Doctus

deleteService(bytes32,bytes32).details: Deletes the Service      Only the Doctus owner can delete the Service

getDoctusById(bytes32).details: Get the Doctus information by ID

returns.found: true if found, false if the ID is not found
returns.members: Array of IDs of the members
returns.services: Array of Service ID under the Doctus

getServiceById(bytes32,bytes32).details: Gets the service information by ID

returns.found: true if found false if not found
returns.id: ID of the Service if found

getServicesForDoctus(bytes32).details: Gets all services for the Doctus

returns.found: return true if found, false if not found
returns.services: Array of Services for th Doctus

listDoctuses().details: Gets the list of all Doctus in the registry

removeDoctusMembers(bytes32,address[]).details: Removes members from the Doctus      Only the owner can remove the members

params.members: Array of members to be deleted

updateService(bytes32,bytes32,bytes).details: Updates the Service      Only the Doctus owner can update the Service

params.sid: Unique ID for the new Service

devdoc.title: Interface for the AI services mnager on Doctrina
